00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,320
What is my wish?

283
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:11,160
You want to use me

284
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,280
to kill Right Knight.

285
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,480
I'm not the one who wants

286
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,000
to kill Right Knight.

287
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,800
It's you.

288
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:45,080
A plant

289
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:49,280
bought you off.

290
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:50,320
Right Knight.

291
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,440
How do you explain that?

292
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,760
Do you know your mistake?

293
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:04,040
I didn't betray you.

294
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:31,600
Father.

295
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,200
Those poisoned by the rosa rubus

296
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,080
aren't aware of it.

297
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:51,840
Right Knight...

298
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:55,040
There's no doubt about Right Knight's loyalty.

299
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,480
Prince Guang's just had unfathomable
ulterior motives.

300
00:18:58,360 --> 00:18:59,560
It's Prince Guang's fault.

301
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,800
Don't blame yourself, Father.

302
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,000
Prince Guang?

303
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:13,240
I'll go and kill him.

304
00:19:14,640 --> 00:19:15,640
I can't believe that he used a plant

305
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,800
to trick you for so many years.

306
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:18,280
He even destroyed
the top martial arts expert

307
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,120
of the Chess of Generals Camp.

308
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,600
You're very powerful
in the imperial court.

309
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:22,840
Even if people with ill intentions

310
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:24,120
want to use the posthumous edict
to create trouble,

311
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:25,600
we can just directly suppress them.

312
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,600
We don't need to worry about it.

313
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,680
Suppress them?

314
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:28,720
How?

315
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,320
Shencai Army's 120,000 troops.

316
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:36,720
They are a bunch of useless people.

317
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,400
They can only fight head-on
with the soldiers

318
00:19:39,400 --> 00:19:40,400
of regional governors

319
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:42,360
and lose to them.

320
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:47,320
Then the Chess of Generals Camp's
500 warriors of sacrifice...

321
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,520
This is

322
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:56,040
a critical moment in my fight

323
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,200
for power with Qi Yan.

324
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,440
Don't do anything to Prince Guang first.

325
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,360
If you do,

326
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,440
it will only let Qi Yan

327
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,960
be reckless and uncontrollable.

328
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:08,640
The timing is not right yet.

329
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,400
Yes.

330
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,280
I was too rash.

331
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:26,960
Your Highness.

332
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,600
Smash them all.

333
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,160
There are more over there.

334
00:20:30,280 --> 00:20:31,240
- They'll only feel at ease this way.
- Yes.

335
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,680
- Smash them all up.
- Yes.

336
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,480
And now,

337
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:34,720
what I need most

338
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,920
is for them to feel at ease.

339
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:42,920
Hurry.

340
00:21:01,340 --> 00:21:06,200
(Xing)

341
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:35,700
(Xing)

342
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,200
You were in the first place?

