379
00:24:48,422 --> 00:24:51,314
♪To me life and death♪

380
00:24:51,347 --> 00:24:54,870
♪Is like the mist and the sky♪

381
00:24:54,972 --> 00:24:58,015
♪Yet it makes us both happy♪

382
00:24:58,109 --> 00:25:01,041
♪Transparent and exquisite♪

383
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,200
Your Majesty.

384
00:25:02,332 --> 00:25:05,099
♪The wind cuts a red thread♪

385
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:06,567
♪The red thread cuts the wind♪

386
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:08,080
His Highness Prince Guang is here.

387
00:25:08,208 --> 00:25:10,894
♪You don't realize the deep feelings♪

388
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,520
Giving out clothes and food

389
