can make them survive for now,

390
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:14,880
but not for a lifetime.

391
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,480
We can imitate Huang Ba

392
00:25:17,120 --> 00:25:18,360
during the Western Han Dynasty.

393
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:21,760
He encouraged minor officials
in the suburbs to raise animals,

394
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,520
then gave them as assistance

395
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,000
to the families of the old, weak,
and poor people.

396
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,160
This is also considered

397
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:29,760
as benefiting the citizens

398
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,280
in the name of
Grand Empress Dowager's birthday.

399
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:32,600
You have

400
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:33,760
thought things through more indeed.

401
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:35,000
Let's do it that way.

402
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:38,560
By the way, Uncle,

403
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:40,640
have you visited her already?

404
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:44,840
Grand Empress Dowager
wasn't feeling well.

405
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:46,240
She couldn't meet with me.

406
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:48,280
I can't disturb her.

407
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:49,800
Your Majesty.

408
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,920
Even if we can't make it extravagant,

409
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:52,960
we must still hold

410
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:54,720
a banquet here.

411
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,520
Only family will be invited

412
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,400
to wish her longevity.

413
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:00,400
Your Majesty.

414
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:02,960
I have a list here.

415
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:03,960
Please check it.

416
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:06,670
(Banquet list)

417
00:26:09,560 --> 00:26:10,600
The Qi family's descendants

418
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:12,600
became a lot fewer

419
00:26:14,800 --> 00:26:15,960
in the past few years.

420
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:17,440
Yes.

421
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,480
It would be great if Princess Ninghe

422
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,560
can return.

423
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:30,360
I heard that Lucong's military
commissioner has already passed away.

424
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,280
I've already asked someone to go
and pay respects.

425
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:33,360
I wonder

426
00:26:34,320 --> 00:26:34,880
if they've met

427
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,960
Aunt Ninghe.

428
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,520
What if we take this opportunity

429
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:41,520
to pick her up and reunite with her?

430
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,080
It's too much trouble.

431
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:45,680
Besides,

432
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:47,080
Duke Chu

433
00:26:47,760 --> 00:26:49,080
won't let her come back.

434
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,640
Your Majesty, Your Highness.

435
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,480
Is the one you're talking about

436
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:55,520
the princess who married

437
00:26:55,520 --> 00:26:56,240
to Lucong?

438
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,240
I heard that when she got married,

439
00:26:58,320 --> 00:26:59,560
she took many musical scores with her.

440
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,960
Even the Violet Bureau
doesn't have them.

441
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:01,880
Your Majesty.

442
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,960
Can you write a letter to her

443
00:27:04,120 --> 00:27:05,480
to ask for a hand-written copy?

444
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,520
Huaizhi.

445
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:07,800
Yes.

446
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:08,680
Didn't you teach your niece

447
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,800
some manners?

448
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:14,000
Your Majesty is right.

449
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,360
What did I do?

450
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,800
What's the matter with you?

451
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,000
His Majesty

452
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:25,160
and His Highness
are having a discussion.

453
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:26,840
Why are you butting in?

454
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:28,200
No, Uncle.

455
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:29,240
There are really many musical scores

456
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:29,920
that we can't find anymore.

457
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:31,000
It would be great

458
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:31,640
if we can find them again.

459
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,720
Why are you worried about that?

460
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,200
Why are you worried about that?

461
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:36,240
Just wait here.

462
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,840
Every day,

463
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,560
I feel so worried.

464
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:45,560
Do you feel happy?

465
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,520
I have a headache.

466
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:50,800
Be happier.

467
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,400
It's rare for the Changming Palace

468
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:54,320
to have someone lively.

469
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,640
That's why my head aches more now.

470
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,240
I don't know

471
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,200
what she's thinking all day long.

472
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:03,040
Uncle.

473
00:28:03,360 --> 00:28:04,000
Let's not talk about her.

474
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:05,920
Here,

475
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:07,120
I think...

476
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:23,520
Left Minister.

477
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,520
I, Yan Xiu, want to consult with you
on something.

478
00:28:25,530 --> 00:28:27,970
(Slow and steady wins the race)

479
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,480
Left Minister!

480
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:35,240
I, Left Advisor Yan Xiu,

481
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,880
want to consult with you on something.

482
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,160
Go away.

483
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:42,240
I'm busy.

484
00:28:43,080 --> 00:28:44,240
This is the exciting part.

485
00:28:46,920 --> 00:28:47,600
Fine.

486
00:28:51,010 --> 00:28:56,670
(Library)

487
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:58,840
You answer the Chess Overseer
if she asks you.

488
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,040
You want me to get out
when I do the asking.

489
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:01,160
Left Minister.

490
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,120
The difference in your treatment

491
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,000
is too obvious.

492
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,520
We can't find the people
from Yuzhen Hall.

493
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:08,120
We can't find out the poison

494
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:09,040
on the assassin's needle either.

495
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:12,640
Which poison is it exactly?

496
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:14,680
Let me see.

497
00:29:15,610 --> 00:29:17,850
(Chess of Generals Camp, Left Knight)

498
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:19,720
Left Knight.

499
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,600
How dare you come back here!

500
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,120
It's been a while, Left Advisor.

501
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,760
Have you been well?

502
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,160
Where's the needle?

503
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,000
What do you think?

504
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:46,720
Can you tell?

505
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:49,280
I got it.

506
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:50,480
Come.

507
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,120
Take a look.

508
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:55,760
Well...

509
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:57,880
It seems like the gloves are a bit old.

510
00:29:58,600 --> 00:30:00,280
I must sew them again.

511
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:01,560
I...

512
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:04,320
Can you take care of official business?

513
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:05,600
Which poison is on the needle?

514
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,440
I can't tell looking at it this way.

515
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:09,280
What should we do then?

516
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,280
This is what we'll do.

517
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,960
Get me ten people.

518
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:17,040
Five men and five women

519
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:20,280
age 10, 20, 30,

520
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,720
50, and 70.

521
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,440
I'll try the poison on different ages

522
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,680
and genders.

523
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,640
We'll know the answer in a few days.

524
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,600
You're scarier than you were

525
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:34,680
a few months ago indeed.

526
00:30:36,600 --> 00:30:37,320
By the way,

527
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,000
where did you go
during this period of time?

528
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:42,280
I failed in getting
the Chess Overseer position,

529
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,320
so I traveled around to feel better.

530
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,480
Do you feel better now?

531
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,720
Exactly the opposite,

532
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:52,320
especially when I found out

533
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:53,080
that Right Knight died

534
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:54,240
in Qiu Yanzhi's hands.

535
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:57,040
I felt much worse.

536
00:30:59,000 --> 00:30:59,600
So go

537
00:30:59,600 --> 00:31:00,760
and inform Qiu Yanzhi

538
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,960
that I'm back.

539
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,480
After being the Chess Overseer
for so long,

540
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,040
she didn't achieve anything.

541
00:31:07,760 --> 00:31:08,640
It's time

542
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:10,840
to replace her.

543
00:31:10,850 --> 00:31:13,700
(Violet Bureau)

544
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:19,360
You may go.

545
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:21,760
Yes.

546
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,080
What did you find?

547
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:34,320
Yuzhen Hall originally has 509 people.

548
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:36,360
Now, they have 277 people.

549
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:37,600
In the past eight years,

550
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,440
they never executed

551
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,320
any real missions.

552
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,280
Those people are gone

553
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,480
due to internal conflict.

554
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:42,520
Do you know

555
00:32:42,520 --> 00:32:44,080
how many people are there
in the Chess of Generals Camp?

556
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:46,560
I don't.

557
00:32:51,560 --> 00:32:52,880
Based on incomplete statistics,

558
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,200
20,000 people were listed.

559
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:56,440
Now,

560
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:59,120
less than 3,000 are left.

561
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:01,840
Do you still think

562
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:04,240
that it's cruel in Yuzhen Hall?

563
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,080
Even so,

564
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:08,640
Yuzhen Hall's training method

565
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:09,800
might not necessarily be right.

566
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,080
I want to go to Mount Qi

